VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:InAppBrowser|cordova\.InAppBrowser|Browser\.open)\s*\(
WHEN EXPR MISSING:validate|allowlist|trusted|Capacitor\.Platform|test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects embedded browser opening flows that need URL allowlist validation.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Insecure Browser Plugin Usage.
